    Static methods for reading or writing cleartext keysets.

    WARNING

    Reading or writing cleartext keysets is a bad practice, usage of this API should be restricted. Users can read encrypted keysets using KeysetHandle.read(com.google.crypto.tink.KeysetReader, com.google.crypto.tink.Aead).
